<section class="webdev-why">
  <div class="webdev-why__inner">
    <div class="webdev-why__header">
      <h2 class="webdev-why__title">Built around how guests actually find you</h2>
      <p class="webdev-why__subtitle">
        A beautiful website is great. A beautiful website that loads fast, is easy
        to update and is built around bookings is even better.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="webdev-why__grid">
      
      <div class="webdev-why__card">
        
        <h3 class="card-title">Optimised for mobile</h3>
        <p class="card-body">
          Most diners discover you on their phone. We design from a mobile-first
          perspective so key actions like booking, calling and viewing the menu
          are always one tap away.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="webdev-why__card">
        
        <h3 class="card-title">SEO-ready structure</h3>
        <p class="card-body">
          Clean page structure, fast loading and thoughtful copy placeholders
          help you rank for local searches like “best Italian in Perth” or
          “rooftop cocktail bar”.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="webdev-why__card">
    
        <h3 class="card-title">Easy to update</h3>
        <p class="card-body">
          We build with a simple, repeatable page structure so you can keep menus,
          events and photography galleries up to date without needing a developer
          for every change.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Section Background */
  .webdev-why {
    background-color: #fef8eb;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem; /* Vertical | Horizontal */
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e3d4b4;
  }

  .webdev-why__inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Header Text */
  .webdev-why__header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem auto;
  }

  .webdev-why__title {
    font-family: "Abril Fatface", serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #152705;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .webdev-why__subtitle {
    font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #24360f;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Grid Layout */
  .webdev-why__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); /* 3 Equal Columns */
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  /* Individual Card Style */
  .webdev-why__card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(227, 212, 180, 0.6);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(21, 39, 5, 0.03);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .webdev-why__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(21, 39, 5, 0.08);
  }


  /* Card Typography */
  .card-title {
    font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #152705;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .card-body {
    font-family: "Darker Grotesque", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #4a5e3a;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Mobile Responsiveness */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .webdev-why__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Stack vertically on tablet/mobile */
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .webdev-why__title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>